origin.moonlight.blood_stalker.descripti: The Bloodstalker is a bizarre and alien arthropod that may be most closely compared to a spider, but even that is not very accurate.
origin.moonlight.blood_stalker.name: Bloodstalker
origin.moonlight.harpy.description: A creature of the skies, the Harpy is an expert in combat and can easily overwhelm an unprepared enemy.
origin.moonlight.harpy.name: Harpy
origin.moonlight.moobloom.description: A cow grown from the ground, surrounded and shrouded in dandelions. It roams the Earth serving melatonin to others.
origin.moonlight.moobloom.name: Moobloom
origin.moonlight.power_armor.description: You're a human equipped with your own personal infantry combat technology.
origin.moonlight.power_armor.name: Power Armor
origin.moonlight.robobot.description: A robot built by a megam-- m-mastermind. Intelligence and effectiveness varies based on its upgrade version.
origin.moonlight.robobot.name: Robobot
origin.moonlight.shark.name: Shark
origin.moonlight.snake.name: Sneaky Snake
origin.moonlight.snow_leopard.descriptio: Despite being a loner, a scavenger in the frozen wastes just trying to get by, you've always wanted to improve this world. No matter what it takes; no matter the cost...
origin.moonlight.snow_leopard.name: Snow Leopard
power.moonlight.blood_stalker.armor.desc: You can't use netherite armor, as it makes you too heavy to use your webs.
power.moonlight.blood_stalker.armor.name: Overburdened
power.moonlight.blood_stalker.blood.desc: You can't eat normal food, instead you can only feast upon the blood of other creatures.
power.moonlight.blood_stalker.blood.name: Sanguivore
power.moonlight.blood_stalker.climb.desc: You have the ability to climb walls, for better or for worse.
power.moonlight.blood_stalker.climb.name: Spider Legs
power.moonlight.blood_stalker.grapple.de: You can grab onto other creatures and drink their blood.
power.moonlight.blood_stalker.sense.desc: During the night, you gain spidey senses =]
power.moonlight.blood_stalker.sense.name: Danger Sense
power.moonlight.blood_stalker.size.descr: You're slightly larger than other spiders.
power.moonlight.blood_stalker.size.name: Primordial Form
power.moonlight.blood_stalker.sling.desc: You can shoot a string of web to pull yourself, or others.
power.moonlight.blood_stalker.sling.name: Web Sling
power.moonlight.harpy.backpedal.descript: You can leap backwards and up into the air to evade attacks.
power.moonlight.harpy.backpedal.name: Backpedal
power.moonlight.harpy.elytra.description: You may fly, however it can be exhausting.
power.moonlight.harpy.elytra.name: Winged
power.moonlight.harpy.flap.description: Your wings are strong, allowing you to fly further and for longer periods of time.
power.moonlight.harpy.flap.name: Powerful Wings
power.moonlight.harpy.flimsy.description: You have reduced health and take more damage overall.
power.moonlight.harpy.flimsy.name: Brittle Build
power.moonlight.harpy.perch.description: You can perch on the heads of others.
power.moonlight.harpy.perch.name: Unwanted Landing
power.moonlight.harpy.sharp_claws.descri: Your unarmed attacks deal extra damage, and you deal even more damage while flying.
power.moonlight.harpy.sharp_claws.name: Sharp Claws
power.moonlight.harpy.size.name: Bird-like Body
power.moonlight.harpy.soaked.description: Rain makes it incredibly hard for you to fly, and can even be deadly. This can be remedied by sitting near warmth.
power.moonlight.harpy.soaked.name: Hydrophobic
power.moonlight.harpy.steal.description: You're able to snatch the items of others right out of their hands.
power.moonlight.harpy.steal.name: Sleight of Talons
power.moonlight.harpy.weak_legs.descript: While not mid-air, your movement speed is decreased.
power.moonlight.harpy.weak_legs.name: Grounded
power.moonlight.moobloom.flower_trail.de: You leave a trail of dandelions as you walk.
power.moonlight.moobloom.hide.name: One with Nature
power.moonlight.moobloom.milk_bucket.des: Right-clicking while sneaking and holding a bucket will fill it with milk.
power.moonlight.moobloom.no_netherite.de: Netherite armor is too heavy for you to wear.
power.moonlight.moobloom.regen.descripti: Nearby players are given a small dose of melatonin and regenerate health more quickly.
power.moonlight.moobloom.regen.name: Passive Dosage
power.moonlight.moobloom.size.descriptio: You're smaller than a normal player, only being 1.5 blocks tall.
power.moonlight.moobloom.size.name: Cow-sized
power.moonlight.moobloom.stomp.descripti: By slamming your feet against the ground, nearby creatures are thrown away from you and take 2 hearts of damage.
power.moonlight.moobloom.stomp.name: Mighty Stomp
power.moonlight.moobloom.vegetarian.desc: You can only eat wheat and plant-based foods, however eating grants you more hunger.
power.moonlight.moobloom.vegetarian.name: Vegetarian
Your body mass makes it difficult to walk while in water.
power.moonlight.power_armor.armor.descri: You don't need anything fancy, just your super-high-tech-nuclear-powered armor suit. Who needs netherite?
power.moonlight.power_armor.armor.name: Personal Armor
power.moonlight.power_armor.bomb.descrip: You can drop one of your fusion cores to create an explosion.
power.moonlight.power_armor.bomb.name: Core Drop
power.moonlight.power_armor.buffs.descri: While wearing your armor, you take less and deal more damage.
power.moonlight.power_armor.buffs.name: Fortified
power.moonlight.power_armor.debuffs.desc: While you aren't wearing your armor, you take more and deal less damage.
power.moonlight.power_armor.debuffs.name: Flimsy
power.moonlight.power_armor.movement.des: While wearing your armor, you move slower unless you have extra power to spare.
power.moonlight.power_armor.oxygen.descr: While underwater, your oxygen reserves can keep you breathing. At least for a little while.
power.moonlight.power_armor.oxygen.name: O2 Canisters
power.moonlight.power_armor.power.descri: Your armor runs off of Fusion Cores and has an electrical reserve that can power your suit.
power.moonlight.power_armor.power.name: Fusion Power
power.moonlight.power_armor.scale.descri: Your armor makes you slightly taller than the average player.
power.moonlight.power_armor.scale.name: Compensating, huh?
power.moonlight.power_armor.state.descri: You can get in and out of your armor at will, but it takes a bit of time.
power.moonlight.power_armor.state.name: Heavy Equipment
power.moonlight.shark.drought.descriptio: Gain nausea, deal half the amount of damage, and lose the ability to sprint in hot biomes (including the nether).
power.moonlight.shark.drought.name: Drought
power.moonlight.shark.frenzy.description: Press secondary to gain increased attack damage, speed, and haste for a limited time. This drains you, however, making you swim slower and deal less damage for a short time afterwards.
power.moonlight.shark.frenzy.name: Hungry Shark
power.moonlight.shark.guts.description: Your attack damage increases by 1.25x when poisoned or withering.
power.moonlight.shark.guts.name: Guts
power.moonlight.shark.health.description: You have 8 hearts, but gain 2x experience.
power.moonlight.shark.health.name: Live Fast, Die Young
power.moonlight.shark.moist.description: You cannot be set on fire, but take 2x damage from lava.
power.moonlight.shark.moist.name: Moist Skin
power.moonlight.shark.netherite.descript: Your wet body counters the harsh heat of netherite. Deal 2x damage to people wearing netherite armor, however you are incapable of using it yourself.
power.moonlight.shark.netherite.name: Cool Touch
power.moonlight.shark.predator.descripti: Entities nearby gain a speed boost.
power.moonlight.shark.predator.name: Predator
power.moonlight.shark.ravenous.descripti: Only gain 1 bar of saturation from all food.
power.moonlight.shark.ravenous.name: Ravenous
power.moonlight.shark.ruthless.descripti: Attacking someone disables their natural regeneration for 5 seconds.
power.moonlight.shark.ruthless.name: Ruthless
power.moonlight.shark.swim.name: Swift Swimmer
power.moonlight.snake.agony.description: You're an infiltrator, not a front-lines soldier. You take extra damage from projectiles.
power.moonlight.snake.agony.name: Not a Footsoldier
power.moonlight.snake.alert.description: When taking damage, your prescense is alerted to everyone. Receive glowing for 3 seconds when hit.
power.moonlight.snake.alert.name: Spotted!
power.moonlight.snake.barrel.description: Crawl your way around in style!
power.moonlight.snake.barrel.name: Sneak 100
power.moonlight.snake.coil.description: You can gently wrap around peoples necks, non-lethally using them as a free ride.
power.moonlight.snake.coil.name: Coil
power.moonlight.snake.fall.description: You're constantly moving around and falling from heights, so you take no damage from falling.
power.moonlight.snake.fall.name: Soft Landing
power.moonlight.snake.heal.description: After taking damage, you will not start regenerating until standing still and sneaking for 5 seconds. After this, you regenerate slightly faster than normal.
power.moonlight.snake.heal.name: Slow Healer
power.moonlight.snake.heavy.description: If wearing anything other than chainmail or leather armor, all stealth abilities are disabled and you move slower.
power.moonlight.snake.heavy.name: Too Heavy
power.moonlight.snake.hide.description: You're harder to see in darkness. During the day, you can hide in grass and flowers to stay hidden.
power.moonlight.snake.hide.name: Master of Stealth
power.moonlight.snake.jump.description: You can coil and spring your body to reach greater heights.
power.moonlight.snake.jump.name: Coiled jump
power.moonlight.snake.size.name: Small
power.moonlight.snake.smoke.description: You drop a smoke bomb, blinding anyone near you, allowing for a quick escape. / Fire a beam of light that explodes (without harming) and blinds anything near the explosion.
power.moonlight.snake.smoke.name: Smoke Bomb / Flashbang
power.moonlight.snow_leopard.diet.descri: You're only able to eat soft foods
power.moonlight.snow_leopard.diet.name: Weak Teeth
power.moonlight.snow_leopard.disease.des: Your disease will eventually have you succumb to a slow and painful death.
power.moonlight.snow_leopard.health.desc: Typically you'd have nine lives, but you're so old that you lost one...
power.moonlight.snow_leopard.health.name: Not Quite Nine Lives
power.moonlight.snow_leopard.jump.descri: You might be old and your knees are giving out, but at least you have your moon shoes!
power.moonlight.snow_leopard.jump.name: Moon Shoes
power.moonlight.snow_leopard.speed.descr: Despite your age, you still haven't lost your touch.
power.moonlight.snow_leopard.speed.name: Biological Advantage
